'''Martin Wixted''' was the author of ''[[Galaxy Guide 7: Mos Eisley]]''. He also wrote two articles that appeared in the science fiction magazine [[Challenge (magazine)|''Challenge'']], "[[HoloNet Waystation (article)|HoloNet Waystation]]" (in [[Challenge 74|#74]]) and "[[New Character Templates: A Supplement to Star Wars' Mos Eisley Galaxy Guide]]" (in [[Challenge 73|#73]]), the second of which was an addendum to ''Galaxy Guide 7.''

